    {
      "id": "detailed_2_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_2",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and serves as a reliable daily driver, though it shows clear signs of its age. The exterior has several noticeable scratches and a small dent on the rear passenger door, and the interior upholstery exhibits some staining and wear on the driver's seat. Mechanically, the car runs and drives well, but it will likely need new tires and a brake service in the near future. It is a solid choice for someone looking for a functional vehicle who doesn't mind a few cosmetic imperfections.",
